            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ar</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius Ve<lb break="no" n="2"/>rus Maximinus In<lb break="no" n="3"/>victus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius <lb n="4"/>Verus Maximus <expan><abbr>nobil</abbr><ex>issimus</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ar</ex></expan> opus porticus fori <lb n="6"/>et aedibus cum hodio <note>sic</note> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>vetust</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> dilapsum <expan><abbr>pec</abbr><ex>unia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pub</abbr><ex>lica</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Cosanor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>rest</abbr><ex>itui</ex></expan> iusserunt <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>am</ex></expan> agente <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Rufio <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>Proculo <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Tafel besteht aus vielen Fragmenten. Zum Vater des Senators s. CIL XI 2997; XV 7525. Die Tafel stammt ursprünglich vom Forum. Für odeo steht hodio. Datierung: nach der Zeit zwischen dem 7.1. und 16.5.236 n. Chr. (Maximus zum Caesar erhoben) und Mitte Januar 238 n. Chr. (Maximinus Thrax und Maximus zu hostes erklärt). Material: lunensischer Marmor.</p>
            </div>
